import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import SignUpForm from './index'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"signupform"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#signupform"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`SignUpForm`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={SignUpForm} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h2" props={{"aria-hidden":true,"href":"#basic-usage"}}><MDXTag name="span" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"className":"icon-link"}}>{`#`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __code={`<SignUpForm />`} __scope={{props,SignUpForm}}>
  <SignUpForm  />
</Playground></MDXTag>
